'''2018年亚洲室内田径锦标赛'''是第8届[[亚洲室内田径锦标赛|亚洲室内田径锦标赛]]，于2018年2月1日至3日在伊朗德黑兰进行，这是德黑兰第三次主办亚洲室内田径锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1060886/barshim-the-star-name-as-tehran-hosts-asian-indoor-athletics-championships|title=Barshim the star name as Tehran hosts Asian Indoor Athletics Championships|work=Inside the Games|date=2018-01-31|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201005813/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1060886/barshim-the-star-name-as-tehran-hosts-asian-indoor-athletics-championships|archivedate=2018-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.irna.ir/news/82816493/8th-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championships-kicks-off-in-Tehran|title=8th Asian Indoor Athletics Championships kicks off in Tehran|publisher=Islamic Republic News Agency|date=2018-02-01|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200928164911/https://en.irna.ir/news/82816493/8th-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championships-kicks-off-in-Tehran|archivedate=2020-09-28}}</ref>。

哈萨克斯坦以7金4银1铜的成绩位列奖牌榜榜首，主办国伊朗以5金9银10铜位列次席，上届比赛位列奖牌榜榜首的卡塔尔队则以4金3银2铜位居第三位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.athleticsasia.org/kazakhstan-emerged-top-in-the-8th-asian-indoor-athletics-championship-tehran-2018/|title=Kazakhstan emerged top in the 8th Asian Indoor Athletics Championship Tehran 2018|work=Asian Athletics Association|date=2019-11-07|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326093908/http://www.athleticsasia.org/kazakhstan-emerged-top-in-the-8th-asian-indoor-athletics-championship-tehran-2018/|archivedate=2020-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tehrantimes.com/news/420974/Iran-runners-up-at-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championships|title=Iran runners-up at Asian Indoor Athletics Championships|publisher=Tehran Times|date=2018-02-04|accessdate=2020-09-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316133742/http://www.tehrantimes.com/news/420974/Iran-runners-up-at-Asian-Indoor-Athletics-Championships|archivedate=2018-03-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

